## ğŸ¬ Demo & Examples

### Live Visualization
Visit the [CodePen demo](https://codepen.io/Cosimos-Portinari/pen/zxqVpEv) to see:
- Interactive calendar wheel
- Animated pentagram
- Month highlighting
- Responsive design
- Mobile-friendly interface

### Code Example: Date Calculation
```javascript
// Convert day of year to month/day
function getMonthAndDay(dayOfYear) {
    const DAYS_PER_MONTH = 27;
    const month = Math.floor((dayOfYear - 1) / DAYS_PER_MONTH) + 1;
    const day = ((dayOfYear - 1) % DAYS_PER_MONTH) + 1;
    return { month, day };
}

// Check if day is Sacred Day
function isSacredDay(dayOfYear) {
    const SACRED_DAYS = [72, 144, 216, 288, 360];
    return SACRED_DAYS.includes(dayOfYear);
}

// Example usage
const result = getMonthAndDay(100);
console.log(`Day 100 is Month ${result.month}, Day ${result.day}`);
// Output: "Day 100 is Month 4, Day 19"
```

